trans-unit.source: Provides a way to translate property values between [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] controls and [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] elements.
trans-unit.target: Fornece uma maneira de converter valores de propriedade entre [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winforms](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] controles e [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_winclient](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] elementos.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap"></xref> class with the given source object.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap"> </xref> classe com o objeto de origem especificado.

trans-unit.source: `source` is the source of the properties which are translated by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>.
trans-unit.target: `source`é a origem das propriedades que são convertidas pelo <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>

trans-unit.source: The properties which are mapped in the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap> must exist on <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap.SourceObject%2A>.
trans-unit.target: As propriedades que estão mapeadas em que <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>deve existir no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap.SourceObject%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap.SourceObject%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator> delegates are called using the current property values on <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap.SourceObject%2A>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator>delegados são chamados usando os valores de propriedade atuais em <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap.SourceObject%2A>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap.SourceObject%2A></xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator>

trans-unit.source: The object which has the properties to be translated.
trans-unit.target: O objeto que tem as propriedades a serem convertidos.

trans-unit.target: Adiciona um <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator"> </xref> delegar para a propriedade especificada para o <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: When setting, if no <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator> exists for `propertyName`, the new delegate is added to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>.
trans-unit.target: Durante a configuração, se nenhum <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator>existe para `propertyName`, o representante novo é adicionado a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMap> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyTranslator>

trans-unit.target: O nome da propriedade para mapear.

trans-unit.target: Executa o tradutor de propriedade para cada propriedade mapeada, com base em valores de propriedade do objeto de origem atual.

trans-unit.target: Para obter uma lista de mapeamentos de propriedade padrão, consulte [formulários do Windows e o mapeamento de propriedade do WPF](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Occurs when an exception is raised by a property translator.
trans-unit.target: Ocorre quando uma exceção é gerada por um tradutor de propriedade.

trans-unit.source: Handlers for the PropertyMappingError event can optionally raise the exception by setting the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.IntegrationExceptionEventArgs.ThrowException%2A> flag on the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMappingExceptionEventArgs>.
trans-unit.target: Manipuladores para o evento PropertyMappingError opcionalmente podem aumentar a exceção, a definição do <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.IntegrationExceptionEventArgs.ThrowException%2A>sinalizador em <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMappingExceptionEventArgs>.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.PropertyMappingExceptionEventArgs> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.Integration.IntegrationExceptionEventArgs.ThrowException%2A>
